attributes.Long form description: First, the student detaches the lens from the DSLR with the instructor's help. Next, the student attaches the lens but has problems doing it and the instructor helps to finish this task. After a while, once the lens was attached, the student removes the lens cover from the lens of the DSLR. Then, the student attaches the lens cover again. Next, the student turns on and then turns off the DSLR. After that, the student exchanges the battery from the DSLR for a new one. Lastly, the student exchanges the SD card of the DSLR for a new one.
